{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act33side_level_act33side_02_end","storyGroup":"act33side","storySort":5,"storyDependence":"act33side_level_act33side_02_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BB-2","storyName":"命途何在","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"卡兹戴尔突入天灾摆脱追击。特雷西斯在风暴中收留了一个荒野上的孩子，并为她取名“阿斯卡纶”。而一个自称“曼弗雷德”的少年找到了特蕾西娅和特雷西斯。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act33side/level_act33side_02_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act33side_02","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":3,"next":5,"characters":["特雷西斯","特蕾西娅","？？？","激动的萨卡兹","巴别塔医生","阴郁的萨卡兹","阿斯卡纶","勇敢的孩子","迷糊的孩子","好运","奥达"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_bg_bg_laccolith.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$epic_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_bat_epic_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowstormflp","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":7},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":8},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":10},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":11},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":13},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我们站在这艘军舰的辙印旁竟显得如此渺小。","id":15},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"是啊，令人惊叹的军事器械。","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"食腐者的血肉防线付出极大代价才阻截了战舰的行进，女妖足以撕碎意识的尖啸也仅仅是逼迫他们舍弃舰桥，撤往下层的指挥中心......","id":18},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"如果不是天灾在前，加之这块峡谷地带的险要地势——","id":20},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我们的时间真的不多了。","id":22},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"卡兹戴尔必须拥有同样的，甚至超越他们想象的武器。","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我们迄今为止的尝试都失败了......","id":26},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"百多年前，谁又相信我们能够将卡兹戴尔真的建成移动城市呢？循规蹈矩无法让卡兹戴尔追上那些国家的步伐。","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"变形者刚传回了消息，地平线上与我们遥遥相望的军舰都已经开始减速了。","id":29},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"他们放弃了？","id":31},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"不。选帝侯发出的指令是继续追击，但是舰队的指挥下达了减速的指令。","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"他们在害怕天灾和恶劣的地形，我们眼前这艘军舰就是前车之鉴。","id":34},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"那按照他们的前进速度，傍晚就是决战的时候了。","id":36},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......足够了，我们已经拖延了充足的时间。","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":39},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅回望荒野上两股逐渐纠缠的风暴，试图找寻那座庞大城市的踪迹。","id":40},{"type":"text","text":"一无所获。卡兹戴尔如今已经到了哪里？它是否仍然在风暴中迁徙？躲藏在庇护所中的居民是否依旧安好？","id":41},{"type":"dialog","id":42},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":43},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":44},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"那两股风暴开始聚拢了，我们的后路已经被彻底堵上了。决战不可避免，无论如何......特雷西斯？","id":46},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......","id":48},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你竟然会在战场上走神。","id":50},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......那是什么？","id":52},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......？","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"那是......","id":55},{"type":"dialog","id":56},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":57},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":58},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":59},{"type":"charslot","id":60},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":61},{"type":"image","image":"49_i03_2","screenadapt":"coverall","id":62},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.1","yScaleTo":"1.1","duration":"50","id":63},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$chenandwei_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act14d0d0/m_avg_chenandwei_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":64,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sandstorm","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":65},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.3","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"20","id":66},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":67},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":68},{"type":"text","text":"风暴在发怒，年幼者正张扬着挑衅年长者。","id":69},{"type":"text","text":"新生的风暴裹挟着雷鸣撞向了奄奄一息的风暴。","id":70},{"type":"text","text":"紊乱的空气流在两股风暴之间交错，融合......","id":71},{"type":"text","text":"狂暴孕育平静。一条狭长的通路诞生于风暴交汇之处。","id":72},{"type":"text","text":"电光闪耀，雷鸣回荡。","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"一条路，在风暴之中。","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"风暴......","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"特蕾西娅，走吧，道路已被风暴铸下。","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"活下来的人还有另一条路可以选。","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我们一起。","id":78},{"type":"text","text":"他们的命令在下一刻便由变形者集群传到每一位在场萨卡兹的耳中。","id":79},{"type":"text","text":"战士们看到了两位领袖并肩走入风暴。无人迟疑，所有人动了起来。","id":80},{"type":"text","text":"健全者搀扶虚弱者，勇敢者鼓励畏怯者。漫漫长队迈入了风暴。","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......特雷西斯，你看到了吗？","id":82},{"type":"text","text":"风暴的呼啸中，那道源自幼时梦中风雪的声音仿佛传入了他们的耳中。","id":83},{"type":"text","text":"他们看到了——","id":84},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.2","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":85},{"type":"image","image":"49_i03_1","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"3","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","id":86},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","duration":"20","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......预言。","id":88},{"type":"text","text":"裹在披风下的瘦弱身影听到了身后的声音，转身回望，看到了迎风而行的队伍。","id":89},{"type":"text","text":"特雷西斯看到了一个孩子。薄暮般的烟雾拥着她的肩头，在风暴中升腾，流淌，向着高空狂啸。","id":90},{"type":"text","text":"特雷西斯摘下手甲，赤手没入烟中。","id":91},{"type":"text","text":"烟雾散去，他被血丝染红的手握住了孩子的石刃。","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（含糊不清的发音）你......啊......抓！抓到！","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你为什么在这？","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（含糊不清的发音）家。你......家！家！","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（含糊不清的发音）你！闯进！家！","id":96},{"type":"text","text":"孩子用力从特雷西斯手中抽出石刃，随后又指向他，向他身后漫长的队伍宣战。","id":97},{"type":"text","text":"生于荒野，无惧荒野，孩子的刀下，人与野兽无异。","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你想杀我？","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（含糊不清的发音）煞，撒......杀，你！","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"没有人教过她怎么说话。她只是模仿着过路人的声音而已。","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......特雷西斯？","id":102},{"type":"text","text":"特雷西斯俯瞰着瘦削的生命，他沉默着。","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"刀，该这么拿。","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（含糊不清的发音）你！","id":106},{"type":"text","text":"孩子看着特雷西斯伸出的手，犹豫片刻后便将钝刃放在了他的手上。","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（含糊不清的发音）......我。你！带，我......带上，我！","id":108},{"type":"text","text":"特雷西斯看到了特蕾西娅的眼神。","id":109},{"type":"text","text":"预言。","id":110},{"type":"text","text":"“弑君之刀剑，诛王之枪矛。”","id":111},{"type":"text","text":"可他们从未在乎过预言。","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"好。","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"跟我们走。萨卡兹的家不在荒野。","id":114},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":115},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":116},{"type":"dialog","id":117},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"charslot","id":119},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":120},{"type":"image","id":121},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":122},{"type":"text","text":"“你有名字吗？”","id":123},{"type":"text","text":"“名字？‘我’。”","id":124},{"type":"text","text":"“那从现在起，你有新的名字了。”","id":125},{"type":"text","text":"“阿斯卡纶。”","id":126},{"type":"dialog","id":127},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":128},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":130,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":131},{"type":"text","text":"十天后","id":132},{"type":"text","text":"卡兹戴尔地区，卡兹戴尔移动城市","id":133},{"type":"dialog","id":134},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_churchfire","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":135},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.5","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"1","id":136},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":137},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"5","id":138},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_934_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":139},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"医生，快看！熔炉重燃了！","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":142},{"type":"dialog","id":143},{"type":"playsound","key":"$smallearthquake","id":144},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"2.5","xstrength":"6","ystrength":"3","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":145},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":146},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"动了？是城市终于开始动了？嘶......","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":149},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_499_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":150},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":151},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"小心点！我才刚刚给你包扎好了伤口......","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"医生，我得赶去熔炉那里。熔炉重燃，卡兹戴尔还在航行......","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"那些莱塔尼亚人没能杀死我们！","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"......","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"呃，我，我不是说你，医生。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"和我一起出去看看吧，你应该和那些活下来的战士享受同样的荣誉。","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"我......不是萨卡兹。","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"但现在不一样了，你们也是英雄，医生。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"去参观两位殿下指挥歌利亚们支撑着的倾斜的熔炉！去看看铁锤修复破损核心时漫天的火星！","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"还能去听听女妖的挽歌，死去英雄的尸体还会被放进熔炉里当做柴薪！","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"过去这可是只有萨卡兹才配参加的庆典。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"我很想去，但今晚还有很多伤员等着处理呢。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"......哎，好吧好吧！这样，我去偷偷带两瓶酒回来，还有新鲜的水果，我们在这里......","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"你哪能喝酒！而且哪有在医疗帐篷里喝酒的！","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"小伤而已，怎么不能？","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"那也不行，现在你的矿石病情况比外伤严重多了！而且你酒量太差了！","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"啊？你哪次看见过我喝酒......哦，我扛着那几个矿石病炸弹来找你的时候。","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"这么多年了，我就那一次喝过酒。平时喝不起，你也不是不知道。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"唉......我拦不住你，你自己去庆典不就好了吗？","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"没了你少点滋味。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"......我......但我毕竟是莱塔尼亚人......","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"怎么，难道你是支持那些靠战争捞钱的贵族老爷的？","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"我就是看不起他们，才从家里逃了出来的！","id":191,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"那就对了。嗯？等等，从家里逃出来，你难道是贵族——","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"不算！","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"可第一次见面我就在想，你的设备明显不是巴别塔掏的钱——","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"——算了，我不乱猜了。对你没好处。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"所以，你自己去就好了。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"我不觉得前线的士兵能和一个莱塔尼亚人和平相处......","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"小时候看我爹被莱塔尼亚人吊在下水道口羞辱的时候，我也没想过能和一个卡普里尼医生和平相处。","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"那时候，唯一会给我们好脸色的，不是感染者，就是贫民。","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"......","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_499_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"激动的萨卡兹","text":"好。不矫情了，我去去就回。","id":208,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":209},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":210},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-200,0","duration":"1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":211},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":212},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"真是，怎么这段时间这群萨卡兹一个个都变得这么油腔滑调......","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"......特蕾西娅小姐，我这也能算是更进了一步吗？","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"总之，呼，卡兹戴尔动起来了，以后总会好起来的。","id":216},{"type":"dialog","id":217},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":218},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":219},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":220},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"嗯？你回来就给我躺下——","id":222},{"type":"dialog","id":223},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":224},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","duration":"1","posfrom":"-100,0","posto":"0,0","id":225},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":226},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"啊，抱歉......认错人了。","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"——","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"等等，你的伤很严重......法术灼烧的位置一直没人帮你处理？","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":233},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":234,"musicid":3},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"莱塔尼亚人干的。我的儿子死了，他们当着我的面把他活活烧死。就活了我一个。","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"......让我看看你的伤口。","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"活活烧死。他在喊，在惨叫。他被法术悬挂在空中，烧给所有人看。","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"我的兄弟也死了，队长也死了。莱塔尼亚人身居高处，制高点，他们高举法杖的样子就像......","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":241},{"type":"text","text":"几乎精神错乱的萨卡兹盯着医生放在角落的莱塔尼亚法杖。","id":242},{"type":"text","text":"她已经放弃的家乡，仍旧以标识的形式悬挂在法杖上。","id":243},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"就像，真正的......","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":246},{"type":"text","text":"医生没有察觉到敌意。","id":247},{"type":"text","text":"她掀开萨卡兹覆盖伤口的衣服，却感受到了一阵寒意。","id":248},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"你带着武器......","id":250},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"......","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","focus":"r","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔医生","text":"外面的守卫为什么没有检查你......","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"l","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"......","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":257},{"type":"dialog","id":258},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":259},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_churchfire","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":260},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"1","id":261},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"text","text":"魂灵熔炉的火光照亮了卡兹戴尔城市之上的整片夜空，恍如白昼。","id":263},{"type":"text","text":"薪柴燃烧的噼啪声如同低沉的嘶吼，祭奠着死去的生命。","id":264},{"type":"text","text":"那一晚，萨卡兹们都不约而同地抬起了头，他们没有看到——","id":265},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"5","id":266},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":267},{"type":"text","text":"城市的一角，一处医疗阵地的灯光静悄悄地黯淡了下去。","id":268},{"type":"dialog","id":269},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":270},{"type":"charslot","id":271},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":272},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":273},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":274},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":275},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":276},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"魔王殿下？","id":278,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"为什么带我来这里......对了，我有好消息要汇报......","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":280},{"type":"charslot","id":281},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#6$1","duration":"0.5","id":282},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"什么消息？","id":284},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"赢了。","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"魔王殿下，我们战胜了莱塔尼亚人，我和我的儿子，还有蓝血小队的所有人，我们赢了，赢了......","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#6$1","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":289},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"......魔王殿下，您不高兴吗？莫非是我们耽搁了战机......","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"布莱克！我的儿子，快把作战计划拿给我看！儿子！儿子？","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"抱歉殿下，我的儿子不知道哪里去了......","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......你杀死了一个医生。一个为卡兹戴尔服务了数年的矿石病医生。","id":296},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"卡兹戴尔？医生？不，殿下，您一定是误会了。","id":298,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"我只会攻击那些莱塔尼亚人。","id":299,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":301},{"type":"dialog","id":302},{"type":"charslot","id":303},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":304},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"特蕾西娅。你感知过他的情绪了吗？","id":306},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#2$1","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"痛苦，混乱，癫狂。他避开了那些惨痛的回忆，逼疯了自己。","id":308},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"他甚至都不知道自己犯下了什么罪。","id":310},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"但是其他人知道。","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"卫兵找到他的时候，他正在和另一个萨卡兹斗殴，酒桶被打碎，劣质酒精被点燃，蔓延到整个医疗阵地。","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"所有人都等着魔王的回应，但这件事不能由你来做。","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"交给我。","id":315},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","id":316},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"殿下，将军，我战胜了莱塔尼亚人，为此献出了一切！","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阴郁的萨卡兹","text":"为什么，难道我做错了？殿下！","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_933_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"把他带下去吧。","id":321},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":323},{"type":"dialog","id":324},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_933_1#1$1","id":325},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","id":326},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"shake","power":"8","times":"50","duration":"0.3","block":"true","id":327},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":328},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":329},{"type":"charslot","id":330},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":331},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":332},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":334},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......他叫洛根。名字是他的母亲取的，他的母亲是巴别塔最初一批工程师中的一员。","id":336},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"他几乎不会使用法术，守卫们却是遭到法术催眠。有其他人在背后推波助澜。","id":338},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"军事委员会不会为了一个外人去调查又一次闯过苦难的萨卡兹们。","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"而我希望，巴别塔也不会。","id":341},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":343},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我们别无他法。战争刚刚结束。","id":345},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我想，这段时间，巴别塔不该再参与任何军政事务。","id":347},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......你知道巴别塔志不在此。","id":349},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"但很多人不这么想。","id":351},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":353},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我会为巴别塔成员划定可以活动的范围。医疗、教育和科技建设，巴别塔将服务于此。","id":355},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"军事委员会对他们的保护仍然生效。但无疑尽量避免冲突才是上策。","id":357},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"被积压的仇恨总有一天会爆发。到那时，即使是我们......即便是我也无能为力。","id":359},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"卡兹戴尔需要尽快迎来一次变革，我们要尽快......克服源石问题。","id":361},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"但这依旧解决不了所有问题，特蕾西娅。","id":363},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我知道。","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我一直知道。","id":366},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":367},{"type":"dialog","id":368},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":369},{"type":"charslot","id":370},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":371},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":372},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":373},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$tech_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_sys_tech_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":374,"musicid":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":375},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":376},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":378},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"阿斯卡纶，你在这。","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你在这座城市里看到了什么？","id":381},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#3$1","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"死......人哭......人死。","id":383},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#10$1","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"哭？哭......哭泣？","id":385},{"type":"charslot","id":386},{"type":"text","text":"特雷西斯伸出手，一柄小巧的石刃躺在他的掌心。","id":387},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#7$1","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"刀！我的......","id":389},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"拿好它，作为战士，应当珍惜自己的武器。","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我会教你如何把它打磨得无比锋利。","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"然后，你要靠自己为它找到正确的方向。","id":393},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#10$1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":395},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"她还没到理解这些事的时候，你太着急了，特雷西斯。","id":397},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"她迟早要明白的，特蕾西娅。","id":399},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"至少现在，我们应该为这个受惊的孩子留一点镇定下来的时间——你喜欢这座城市吗，阿斯卡纶？","id":401},{"type":"charslot","id":402},{"type":"text","text":"比起那个身穿铠甲的将军，阿斯卡纶并不喜欢这个蹲在自己面前的萨卡兹女性。","id":403},{"type":"text","text":"因为她仿佛能读懂自己的一切心思，在她的面前，自己没有任何秘密——这是荒野上生存的大忌。","id":404},{"type":"text","text":"但她却无法对这位温柔的萨卡兹生出敌意。","id":405},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#10$1","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......我......","id":407},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"不用害怕我，你能看到我对你没有敌意，对吗？你可以摸摸我的角，我们是一样的。","id":409},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#1$1","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......这里，温暖。","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"我，温暖。","id":412},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"是的，温暖。仇恨与杀戮并不是解决问题的唯一办法。","id":414},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#10$1","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......（含糊不清的发音）办法？问题？","id":416},{"type":"charslot","id":417},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅没有继续说下去，即使有魔王的帮助，生于荒野的阿斯卡纶也难以理解所有词语。","id":418},{"type":"text","text":"她慢慢捧起了阿斯卡纶的手。","id":419},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......就像你手心的伤口，武器不能让伤口恢复，只有药物和时间才能让它慢慢恢复。","id":421},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#7$1","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"呀啊！","id":423},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"没事了，我已经为你清理了创口，接下来你可要小心照料它。","id":425},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#6$1","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":427},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"耐心些，等到未来某天，当你醒过来，就会发现伤口不再痛了。","id":429},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#8$1","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......嗯！","id":431},{"type":"dialog","id":432},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":433},{"type":"charslot","id":434},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":435},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":436},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":437},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":438},{"type":"text","text":"卡兹戴尔地区，巴别塔教室","id":439},{"type":"dialog","id":440},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":441},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":442},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":443},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":445},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......没人。在。这里。","id":447},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":448},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"再等等，现在还不是上课的时候，他们会来的——","id":449},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":450},{"type":"dialog","id":451},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":452},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":453},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......是你呀，特雷西斯。","id":455},{"type":"dialog","id":456},{"type":"charslot","id":457},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":458},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":459},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"军事委员会递上来一份报告，是关于这次的伤亡情况。其中有很多孩子，大部分也都是学生。","id":460},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"那些活下来的孩子......","id":462},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":463},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"他们的父母不愿意再将他们交到巴别塔的那些外族人老师手里。","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"况且，我记得，巴别塔的不少老师因为害怕已经离开了。","id":465},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#3$1","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......","id":467},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"特蕾西娅，你最近太过操劳这些琐事。你需要休息。我们还需要——","id":469},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我想再等等看，特雷西斯。","id":471},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#2$1","id":472},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......好。","id":473},{"type":"charslot","id":474},{"type":"text","text":"他站在原地，并没有离开，而教室里安静得可怕。","id":475},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅闭上了眼，她回想起了这间教室来来去去的学生们。","id":476},{"type":"dialog","id":477},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":478},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“殿下，他们说上课可以领土豆！”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":479},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“听不懂，殿下，有没有简单的故事？”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":480},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“您说，和我们一般大年纪时，您还跟着佣兵去了外面！”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":481},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“在萨尔贡与伊比利亚之间隔着一道深海？船是什么？禁止我们上甲板？为什么会吐？”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":482},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“莱塔尼亚的高塔？就和我们的熔炉一样吗？”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":483},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“有愿意对我们好的人？骗人，老爹说在外面没有人会那么对我们！”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":484},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“对哦，这里的老师不就对我们很好？”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":485},{"type":"subtitle","id":486},{"type":"text","text":"学生们来了又去，以前她总有办法吸引孩子们回到这间教室。","id":487},{"type":"text","text":"可这一次，没有孩子再来。","id":488},{"type":"dialog","id":489},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":490},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":491},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":492},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......！","id":493},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":494},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"嗯......？","id":495},{"type":"dialog","id":496},{"type":"charslot","id":497},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1302_1#7$1","duration":"0.5","id":498},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":499},{"type":"dialogue","name":"勇敢的孩子","text":"特雷西斯殿下！殿下！我——","id":500},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#4$1","id":501},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"你！","id":502},{"type":"charslot","id":503},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch02","volume":"0.7","id":504},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":505},{"type":"text","text":"一柄石刃的刀柄撞上了孩子的胸口。虽然孩子无法撼动阿斯卡纶的手，但他努力挺起胸膛看着眼前这个瘦高的女孩。","id":506},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1302_1#8$1","id":507},{"type":"dialogue","name":"勇敢的孩子","text":"我看到特雷西斯殿下往这边走，我只是想追上——","id":508},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1302_1#7$1","id":509},{"type":"dialogue","name":"勇敢的孩子","text":"欸，特蕾西娅殿下，您也在！这间教室......是您在上课吗？","id":510},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":511},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"放下刀，阿斯卡纶。","id":512},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#3$1","id":513},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":514},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1302_1#2$1","id":515},{"type":"dialogue","name":"勇敢的孩子","text":"......殿下！","id":516},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","id":517},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你想见我？","id":518},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1302_1#1$1","id":519},{"type":"dialogue","name":"勇敢的孩子","text":"是。我来帮那些失去父母的孩子求一个答案。我知道军事委员会能照顾好他们，就像照顾我一样......","id":520},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1302_1#8$1","id":521},{"type":"dialogue","name":"勇敢的孩子","text":"但是......这会带来任何的变化吗？如果战争又来了呢？","id":522},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1302_1#4$1","id":523},{"type":"dialogue","name":"勇敢的孩子","text":"我想改变，可我不知道可以改变什么，也不知道要去改变什么。","id":524},{"type":"charslot","id":525},{"type":"text","text":"两位殿下看着这位毫无怯意的孩子，他们的心中刹那间都有了各自的答案。","id":526},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":527},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你叫什么名字？","id":528},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1302_1#1$1","id":529},{"type":"dialogue","name":"勇敢的孩子","text":"曼弗雷德。","id":530},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":531},{"type":"dialog","id":532},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":533},{"type":"charslot","id":534},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":535},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":536},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":537},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":538,"musicid":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":539},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":540},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1303_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":541},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":542},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1303_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":543},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷糊的孩子","text":"爸爸，我们已经在家门口站了很久了，为什么不进去呢？","id":544},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":545},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"......","id":546},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"妈妈受了很重很重的伤，她需要一个人在里面休息，我们不该打扰她。","id":547},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1303_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":548},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷糊的孩子","text":"可是我想妈妈了......","id":549},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":550},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"爸爸也想，但是现在不行......等我办完事回来，我们再一起回家。","id":551},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1303_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":552},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷糊的孩子","text":"爸爸要去哪里？","id":553},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":554},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"我要再出一趟城，让那些欺负妈妈的人付出代价。","id":555},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":556},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"你暂时留在这，等爸爸回来。","id":557},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1303_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":558},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷糊的孩子","text":"爸爸可以不走吗？爸爸留在这，我们一起想办法让妈妈好起来......","id":559},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":560},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"你喜欢妈妈的名字吗？","id":561},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1303_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":562},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷糊的孩子","text":"嗯，喜欢，妈妈的名字很好听......奥达。","id":563},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":564},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"以后它就是你的名字了。","id":565},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1303_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":566},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷糊的孩子","text":"可是......","id":567},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":568},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"奥达，等爸爸回来，就教你用妈妈的武器打坏人。","id":569},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1303_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":570},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"好，我要打那些欺负妈妈的坏人！","id":571},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1303_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":572},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥达","text":"可是，打跑了坏人，妈妈的伤就会好起来吗......","id":573},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":574},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"奥达......你还不明白，你以后会明白的。","id":575},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1305_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":576},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好运","text":"......你等我回来。","id":577},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":578},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":579},{"type":"text","text":"好运转身离开了家门口，看向了那堵已被结晶丛林爬满的城墙。","id":580},{"type":"text","text":"如今这座城内足以令他牵挂的只有奥达。","id":581},{"type":"text","text":"那个奥达......还有这个奥达。","id":582},{"type":"dialog","id":583},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":584},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":585},{"type":"image","id":586},{"type":"charslot","id":587}],"characters":["特雷西斯","特蕾西娅","？？？","激动的萨卡兹","巴别塔医生","阴郁的萨卡兹","阿斯卡纶","勇敢的孩子","迷糊的孩子","好运","奥达"]}